dcterms:description: Omniglot consists of 1623 handwritten characters collected from 50 alphabets, with each character including 20 instances drawn by different human subjects. The dataset is used for one-shot learning tasks.

dcterms:description: miniImageNet is collected from the larger ILSVRC-12 dataset and consists of 100 classes with 600 examples per class, totaling 60,000 color images. It is used for few-shot learning tasks.
